Introduction

Jung Jin Sung is a South Korean singer and dancer under Play M Entertainment. He was a member of project group 1THE9, as well as a pre-debut member of the trainee group PlayM BOYS, which would debut in 2021 as JUST B.

On October 25, 2018, Jung Jin Sung was introduced as a contestant of Under Nineteen with his moving poster. The poster revealed that he was a part of the vocal team. He finished in second place, thus becoming a member of the project group 1THE9.
